The paper discusses cyber resilience, which is a topic related to cybersecurity and computer systems. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CR (Cryptography and Security). The paper also discusses systems engineering and modeling, which suggests that it could also belong to cs.SE (Software Engineering) and cs.SY (Systems and Control). The paper mentions dynamic defense, which is a concept related to artificial intelligence, so it could also belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Finally, the paper discusses cyber resilience as it relates to the cyber infrastructure, which suggests that it could also belong to cs.CY (Computers and Society).
